{
  "stem": "6878.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We slept on the side of the road, and when we came to Kovna, we start walking around to look for a job.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stayed in a [INAUDIBLE], because we were [? halutzing ?] from the [INAUDIBLE], so they accommodate us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got a job when I-- the boss asked me, how much do you want a month?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said to him, whatever you-- whatever you'll offer me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I started off working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in 1937.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I worked myself up very nicely, because I was-- first of all, I was known by the electrical everything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had an electrical business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got well paid, and then in six months time, I earned, already, 140 litas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From 80, I started off for 80 litas, and 80 litas was like one pound ten, South African money, those days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I worked myself up very nicely, and in a short while I worked, I got 240, 300, 350 and so on, until the 22nd of June, 1940.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Russia walked in into Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the [NON-ENGLISH] commissar of the Russian appointed me to be the commissar of the shop.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were 16 people in that business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had seven storerooms of goods in, in the business, spread all over places.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after a couple of months later, I received a letter from the Russian authorities to get rid of my [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was then 27.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I wasn't married then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, being the commissar of the shop, and I went up with a letter to show to my owners of the business, and they started to cry.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went up to the hanger of the wall, and took their jackets, and walked out crying.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
